  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Building back better: Building a federation of agrarian reform beneficiaries organization (ABROs) in northern Cebu to lobby for community driven disaster recovery programs by duty bearers</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1a) meetings with each of the ARBOs
1b) ARBOs self-assessments and survey of existing services available and analysis of collected data
1c) General Assembly and consultations withing ARBOs, projected orientation and project launching
1d) Workshop for ARBOs to develop of action plans
1e) ARBOs plan implementation

2a) planning workshop according to clusters and issues identified
2b) creating learning platforms for ARBOs (meetings, role plays, learning visits
2c) Organizing and federation building
2d) training on organizational capacity development 

3a) Dialogues with concerned agencies and other duty bearers
3b) lobby for people&apos;s agenda</narrative>
  </description>
